      <p class="hero-sub">Walk-in coolers, ranges, fryers, ice machines, dishwashers — we keep your kitchen running. Same day available. We know what 41°F means and why it can't wait.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="btn-red">☎ (424) 325-0520</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-outline">Request Service</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-rating"><span class="stars">★★★★★</span> 4.6 · 37 reviews · Google</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-badge-grid">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <div class="hero-badge-icon">🌡️</div>
        <h4>41°F Priority</h4>
        <p>Walk-in failures get same-day dispatch — LADPH compliance, not just convenience</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <div class="hero-badge-icon">📋</div>
        <h4>COI Available</h4>
