      </div>
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <div class="hero-badge-icon">🔩</div>
        <h4>Parts on Truck</h4>
        <p>Vulcan, Garland, True, Manitowoc, Hobart — we stock what LA kitchens run</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <div class="hero-badge-icon">👻</div>
        <h4>Ghost Kitchen Ready</h4>
        <p>We work with delivery-only operations and multi-concept shared kitchens across LA</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST BAR -->
<div class="trust-bar">
  <div class="trust-bar-inner">
    <div class="ti">🏅 CSLB Licensed #1138898</div>
    <div class="ti">🛡️ Fully Insured · COI Available</div>
    <div class="ti">⚡ Same Day Commercial Service</div>
    <div class="ti">📋 Service Documentation Provided</div>
    <div class="ti">💬 $120 Diagnostic — Waived With Repair</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- INTRO -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="body-text">
        <p class="sl">Restaurant & Cafe Service</p>
        <h2>Equipment down means tickets stop. We know that.</h2>
        <p>We get calls from restaurant operators across LA at every hour — a walk-in that stopped holding temp at 2pm before a dinner service, a range igniter that died mid-lunch, an ice machine that stopped making ice on a Friday. These aren't inconveniences. They're revenue events with health code implications.</p>
        <p>Same Day Appliance Repair has been working in LA commercial kitchens long enough to understand the difference between a ghost kitchen in the Arts District that runs 18 hours a day on DoorDash volume and a 40-seat brunch spot in Silver Lake with a Sunday crew. The equipment is different. The urgency calculus is different. The brands are different.</p>
        <p>We carry parts for the equipment that actually runs LA kitchens — Vulcan, Garland, True, Turbo Air, Manitowoc, Hobart, Pitco. Our technicians know that when a walk-in isn't holding 41°F, the problem isn't just a broken compressor — it's a LADPH compliance issue with a clock on it. We move accordingly.</p>
        <p>Ghost kitchens get special attention from us. Equipment in shared commercial kitchens runs harder than anywhere else — often 16 to 18 hours a day with no downtime for maintenance. We know the economics of a dead fryer in a ghost kitchen at 6pm on a Saturday.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Restaurant Emergency Line</h3>
        <p>Equipment down? Call now for same-day dispatch.</p>
        <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="cta-phone">☎ (424) 325-0520</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="cta-book">Request Service Online</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Licensed · COI Available · No call center</p>
        <div class="price-mini">
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Commercial diagnostic</span><span class="pm-val">$120</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Applied to repair</span><span class="pm-val">Yes</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">Service documentation</span><span class="pm-val">Included</span></div>
          <div class="pm-row"><span class="pm-label">COI on request</span><span class="pm-val">Available</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EQUIPMENT WE SERVICE -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="sl">Equipment</p>
    <h2>What we repair in LA restaurant kitchens</h2>
    <p class="lead">From the line to the walk-in — we cover the full commercial kitchen. If it runs on gas or electric and it's in a restaurant kitchen, we work on it.</p>
    <div class="equip-grid">
      <div class="equip-card">
        <div class="equip-icon">❄️</div>
        <h3>Walk-In Coolers & Freezers</h3>
        <p>Temperature failures, compressor issues, fan motor failures, door gaskets, evaporator coils. 41°F compliance is not negotiable — we prioritize these calls.</p>
        <p class="equip-brands">True · Norlake · Kolpak · Heatcraft · Hussmann</p>
      </div>
      <div class="equip-card">
        <div class="equip-icon">🔥</div>
        <h3>Commercial Ranges & Ovens</h3>
        <p>Igniter failures, burner issues, temperature control problems, pilot outages, high-BTU calibration. Gas and electric — from 6-burner ranges to combi ovens.</p>
        <p class="equip-brands">Vulcan · Garland · Wolf · American Range · US Range</p>
      </div>
      <div class="equip-card">
        <div class="equip-icon">🧊</div>
        <h3>Commercial Ice Machines</h3>
        <p>Not making ice, slow production, scale buildup from LA's hard water, mold/slime (LADPH issue), water inlet valve failures. Cleaning service available.</p>
        <p class="equip-brands">Manitowoc · Scotsman · Hoshizaki · Ice-O-Matic</p>
      </div>
      <div class="equip-card">
        <div class="equip-icon">🍽️</div>
        <h3>Commercial Dishwashers</h3>
        <p>Not cleaning properly, temperature issues, final rinse failures, door latch problems. LA hard water descaling included. LADPH wash temperature documentation available.</p>
        <p class="equip-brands">Hobart · Champion · Jackson · Winterhalter · CMA</p>
      </div>
      <div class="equip-card">
        <div class="equip-icon">🛢️</div>
        <h3>Commercial Fryers</h3>
        <p>Temperature control failures, thermostat issues, pilot problems, drain valve failures. Gas and electric. We understand fryer downtime on a dinner service.</p>
        <p class="equip-brands">Pitco · Frymaster · Vulcan · Henny Penny</p>
      </div>
      <div class="equip-card">
        <div class="equip-icon">❄️</div>
        <h3>Commercial Refrigerators & Freezers</h3>
